    <div class="two-text-right">For each instructor, redirect <span>$15,000+</span> worth of admin time to higher-value tasks</div>
  </div>
  <div class="img-block">
    <%= image_tag '/img/assets/index/instructor-time.png', alt: 'Instructor time', class: 'image' %>
    <div class="check-list">
      <ul class="check-list-list">
        <li class="check-list-list-item">
          Configure and template programming projects and share them with the class in seconds.
